MBSTU-OSN’s Mission and vision is Build up Technological knowledge based educational youth in Bangladesh. Promote Use of Computer, Internet and Information & Communication Technology by organizing conferences, workshops, short courses, seminars, symposiums and by publishing easy technological books or journal papers or technical works for School & College Student’s by fully free, throughout at Bangladesh. Help in acquisition and interchange of technical knowledge among the poor people and promote social welfare according to the MBSTU-OSN Acts as well as rules & regulations. Build up MBSTU-OSN Group to cooperate with various NGOs and rural area’s poor people and give them knowledge about Computer and Technology. And one of the most important tasks of MBSTU-OSN is given or distributes the open source software to the people at fully free. And give them knowledge about open source software. And other co-curricular activities organizing Programming Contest, IT Fair, IT quiz, Cultural program, sport, debate, tree plantation, Math Olympiad, Science Olympiad, Blood Donation and interdisciplinary technical programs. There have been fifty volunteer member of MBSTU-OSN. MBSTU-OSN has not enough funds for running these activities for whole rural area of Bangladesh. But Bangladesh poor people must need the knowledge about Computer, Technology, and Internet. For this reason MBSTU-OSN organize funds raising project for serve the rural Undevelopment area’s Bangladeshi poor people. Please help us and donate us for MBSTU-OSN funds raising project.
